### Welcome to Dynamic Charts.
On this page you can find useful information and links.

### Download the Application
Open a git prompt locally and type these commands:

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

### Build the Application
Just follow these simple instructions.

### Contribute
If you would like to contribute to the application, you have your work cut out for you.
